title: Various Artist's Vol 6 Glastonbury 2016
description:
I am one of millions of Scottish people, who Emmigrated and now live in 
Europe.   ONLY A few hundred years ago Scotland was a free and independant 
Nation, before it was sold for Land and Gold without the people's consent, by
a handful of ruling elite.

We have tried to break away twice in my lifetime and in the 1970's 
we said YES to Independance in a National Referendum by 5 clear 
percentage points only to have the rules changed after the vote
by Westminster's ENGLISH MP's and Lords.

Hopefully this will happen again for the BritExit Europe Referendum.

The English, quite happy to take away Scotlands right to pass its own
Taxation, Defence and Foreign Policy laws, does not like Europe forcing
them to clean up there beaches or abide by rules to help clean up this
planet, allow the youth the right to live and Work in any other EU Member
state OR standardise living standards and allow the stronger nations help
the weaker ones in Europe.

The ENGLISH and Welsh, Led by Populist Newpapers have turned there backs 
on Fellow Man at a time when the World needs, more than EVER to pull 
together.   

Scotland said YES to remain in Europe by 12% and NOW we must pull apart from 
England to keep our ties, not only with our friends and customers in Europe,
but with the rest of the World.

James in this torrent sums it all up at the start of the track called
Tommorow.  It is marked EXPLICIT because they say to the BritExit voters
.... FUCK YOU

It is NOT TOO LATE ENGLAND.. Do not press that Article 50 Button! Sorry
WALES, but just like our VOTE in Scotland, you don't count.
